    "text": "Helpful Incentives to Restore the Economic Dream Act of 2017 or the HIRED Act of 2017 \n\nThis bill amends the Internal Revenue Code to allow a business-related tax credit for 40% of the first-year wages (up to $6,000) paid to an employee as part of an apprenticeship program registered under the National Apprenticeship Act."
